\lim_{n\to \infty}{2n \choose n}^{\frac{1}{2n}} = 2
2
\binom{2n}{n}
\binom{2n}{k}
\sum\limits_{k=0}^{2n} \binom{2n}{k} = 2^{2n}
\left(\frac{1}{2n+1}\right)^{1/2n} \to 1
n \to \infty
\binom{2n}{n}^{1/2n} \to 2
n \to \infty
\frac{2^{2n}}{2n+1} \le \binom{2n}{n} \le 2^{2n}  \quad\implies\quad 2 \left(\frac{1}{2n+1}\right)^{1/2n} \le \binom{2n}{n}^{1/2n} \le 2
\binom{2n}{n}\sim \frac{4^n}{\sqrt{\pi n}}
\binom{2n}{n}^{\frac{1}{2n}} \sim \left(\frac{4^n}{\sqrt{\pi n}}\right)^{1/(2n)} = 2\cdot (\pi n)^{-\frac{1}{4n}}\rightarrow 2
n\rightarrow\infty
